Description:

输入一个链表，反转链表后，输出链表的所有元素。

leetcode: https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/fan-zhuan-lian-biao-lcof/

思路： pre, cur, next.

solution:
/**
 * Definition for singly-linked list.
 * public class ListNode {
 *     int val;
 *     ListNode next;
 *     ListNode(int x) { val = x; }
 * }
 */
class Solution {
    public ListNode reverseList(ListNode head) {
        ListNode pre = null;
        ListNode cur = head;
        ListNode next = null;

        while(cur != null){
            next = cur.next;
            cur.next = pre;
            
            pre = cur;
            cur = next;

        }
        return pre;

    }
}

总结：
line 25 不可以ListNode next = cur.next; 相当于循环
